Title: Excel to SQL Server Database Bulk Transfer
Description:
Quick and simple WPF tool to allow users export data from an Excel spreadsheet to a SQL Server database table.

Provided as is. But if you need any help let me know.
HomeWiki:
This is not my finest work, but it's main purpose is to provide a quick and simple way to export Excel Worksheets into a SQL Server database table. If you find it useful, enjoy!

You may need the Access Database engine (ACE)

See http://www.microsoft.com/download/en/details.aspx?id=13255

Provided as is. But if you need any help let me know.
